Credibility: The blue check mark adds credibility by verifying the doctor, instilling trust in potential patients. Profile Prominence: Top visibility ensures the doctor\'s profile stands out, increasing the chances of patient selection. Appointment Assurance: Daily assured appointments provide a steady flow of patients, optimizing the doctor\'s schedule. App User Base: Being featured results in more users discovering and engaging with the doctor\'s profile through the app. Specialized Priority: Priority appointment booking across specialties ensures efficient and prompt service for patients.
